40:04.152 --> 40:06.070
And how does that make you feel?

40:07.822 --> 40:09.365
How it makes me feel?

40:10.742 --> 40:11.743
Listen, will.

40:13.077 --> 40:15.788
I only have seven days left here, okay?

40:15.872 --> 40:19.000
