When are we gonna grab a beer together?

40:58.581 --> 40:59.415
A beer?

40:59.499 --> 41:01.876
I saw some bottles in the fridge.
You gotta have a grill.

41:01.960 --> 41:04.337
We can slap some steaks on,
call some chicks.

41:06.631 --> 41:10.009
