45:31.646 --> 45:32.647
I don't get it.

45:33.189 --> 45:34.857
A candidate was eliminated, so...

45:34.941 --> 45:38.319
I asked if there was a moment
he would like to experience.

45:38.861 --> 45:40.196
A last wish.

45:40.279 --> 45:42.240
We're making a moment here.

45:42.323 --> 45:44.617
