- You can sand the wood.

45:53.793 --> 45:56.170
I don't have time
to teach her how to sand.

45:56.254 --> 45:57.463
I can figure it out.

46:01.634 --> 46:03.552
Looks like we got a natural here.

46:09.350 --> 46:10.350
Kyo?

46:11.769 --> 46:13.729
If you could pick a moment,

46:13.813 --> 46:15.439
what moment would you pick?

46:15.523 --> 46:16.523
A moment?

46:17.233 --> 46:19.235
A moment you'd like to experience.

46:21.028 --> 46:22.488
Okay, don't laugh.

46:23.155 --> 46:23.990
I won't.

46:24.073 --> 46:25.073
Well,

46:25.700 --> 46:27.118
in the movies,

46:27.660 --> 46:30.037
